{
  "stem": "26792.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a four or five room apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- That was already away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was already away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This I have-- I have missed that part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there's actually nothing I can say, because we were thrown from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a Dienstmadchen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only as a Dienstmadchen, yes, we all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never knew his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I understood only one thing-- that he was writing a book, that he was a Baltendeutsche-- a German from, from the Baltic states-- who knew Latvian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was writing a book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now and again, I, I glanced at the book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw it is about the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was a baron, an arist-- an aristocrat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he never said-- when he saw me on the few occasions-- he never said good morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He never answered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's a very bad sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I did-- never knew his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't tell you why, because my story makes no sense.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Again, it is intuition, I believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- one day, it occurred to me, I have to steal the key which was hanging on the wall-- a key of the kitchen door.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The, the apartment had two doors-- a front door and a kitchen door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The kitchen door was actually a double door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how great the distance was between the one door and the other one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But at least there was room enough for me to stay there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After having taken the decision to commit suicide, I decided I had to write a, a note to my nanny because I wanted her to know that I was not killed, that I was not dying of rape or what, that I had drowned myself in the Dvina.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A very short note.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
